title: Russia marks 74th anniversary of victory over Nazi Germany in World War II
content: World War II veteran Galina Malysheva (C), 95, talks with others during celebrations of the Victory Day in Moscow, Russia, on May 9, 2019. Russia marks the 74th anniversary of the victory over Nazi Germany in World War II here on May 9. (Xinhua/Alexander Zemlianichenko Jr)
